r Dates. Arrays and dictionaries as values are not supported at this time, and will"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"be dropped."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"params"},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"An optional "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/superwall-ios.SuperwallKit\/documentation\/SuperwallKit\/PaywallOverrides","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" object whose parameters override the paywall defaults. Use this"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to override products and whether it ignores the subscription status. Defaults to "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"nil"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"paywallOverrides"},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"An optional completion block that gets called when the paywall should dismiss. This defaults to "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"nil"},{"type":"text","text":" and the SDK"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"will call "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"presentationMode.wrappedValue.dismiss()"},{"type":"text","text":" by default. Otherwise you must perform the dismissal of the paywall."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"onRequestDismiss"},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"A completion block that accepts a "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/superwall-ios.SuperwallKit\/documentation\/SuperwallKit\/PaywallSkippedReason","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" and returns an "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"View"},{"type":"text","text":". This will show"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"when the requested paywall is skipped. Defaults to "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"EmptyView()"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"onSkippedView"},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"A completion block containing a feature that you wish to paywall. Access to this block is remotely configurable via the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/superwall.com\/dashboard","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":". If the paywall is set to "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Non Gated"}]},{"type":"text","text":", this will be called when"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the paywall is dismissed or if the user is already paying. If the paywall is "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Gated"}]},{"type":"text","text":", this will be called only if the user is already paying"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"or if they begin paying. If no paywall is configured, this gets called immediately. This will not be called in the event of an error."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"feature"}],"kind":"parameters"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"This uses ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Superwall\/getPaywall(forPlacement:params:paywallOverrides:delegate:)"},{"text":" under the hood.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"aside","style":"warning","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"You’re responsible for the deallocation of this view. If you have a "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"PaywallView"},{"type":"text","text":" presented somewhere"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"and you try to present the same "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"PaywallView"},{"type":"text","text":" elsewhere, you will get a crash."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"Warning"}]}],"kind":"symbol","schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/superwall-ios.SuperwallKit\/documentation\/SuperwallKit","doc:\/\/superwall-ios.SuperwallKit\/documentation\/SuperwallKit\/PaywallView"]]},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A SwiftUI paywall view that you can embed into your app."}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/superwallk